      "rendered": "10 Holiday Gift Programs That Benefit Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Gift-Programs-Facebook.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-16920\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Gift-Programs-Facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Gift Programs Facebook\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Gift-Programs-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Gift-Programs-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Gift-Programs-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Gift-Programs-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Gift-Programs-Facebook.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>As a follow-up to\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2014/10/27/25-online-gift-stores-that-benefit-nonprofits/\"><strong>25 Online Gift Stores That Benefit Nonprofit</strong>s</a>, below are 10 holiday gift programs that benefit nonprofits. Gifts range from symbolic adopt-an-acre of a national park gifts to\u00a0funding a classroom project in a low-income community. <span style=\"color: #383838;\">These gift programs are ideal for socially and environmentally conscious holiday shoppers that would prefer their holiday spending directly empower nonprofits. They also make excellent gifts for activists and advocates of global development, environmental conservation, and wildlife protection.\u00a0</span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. World Wildlife Gift Center</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gifts.worldwildlife.org/gift-center/Default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16821\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shop.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gifts.worldwildlife.org/gift-center/Default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16905\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/WWF.png?resize=600%2C352\" alt=\"WWF\" width=\"600\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/WWF.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/WWF.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Wilderness Society Adoption\u00a0Center</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.wilderness.org/site/Ecommerce?store_id=4201&amp;s_src=website&amp;s_subsrc=navigation\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16821\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shop.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.wilderness.org/site/Ecommerce?store_id=4201&amp;s_src=website&amp;s_subsrc=navigation\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16825\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/wilderness-society-catalog.png?resize=600%2C353\" alt=\"wilderness society catalog\" width=\"600\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/wilderness-society-catalog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/wilderness-society-catalog.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Save the Children Gifts of Joy</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gift.savethechildren.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16821\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shop.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gift.savethechildren.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16820\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Save-The-Children-Gifts-of-Joy.png?resize=600%2C394\" alt=\"Save The Children Gifts of Joy\" width=\"600\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Save-The-Children-Gifts-of-Joy.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Save-The-Children-Gifts-of-Joy.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Oceana Marine Wildlife Adoption and Gift Center</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://gift.oceana.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16821 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shop.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://gift.oceana.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16903\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Oceana.png?resize=600%2C327\" alt=\"Oceana\" width=\"600\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Oceana.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Oceana.png?resize=300%2C163&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Heifer International Holiday Gifts</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.heifer.org/gift-catalog/holiday/index.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16821 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shop.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.heifer.org/gift-catalog/holiday/index.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16909\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Heifer.png?resize=600%2C337\" alt=\"Heifer\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Heifer.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Heifer.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Natural Resources Defense Council Green Gifts</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nrdcgreengifts.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16821\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shop.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nrdcgreengifts.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16899\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/NRDC-Gifts.png?resize=600%2C372\" alt=\"NRDC Gifts\" width=\"600\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/NRDC-Gifts.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/NRDC-Gifts.png?resize=300%2C186&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Nature Conservancy Gifts of Nature</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nature.org/membership-giving/more-ways-to-give/green-gifts/index.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14951 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop-now4\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nature.org/membership-giving/more-ways-to-give/green-gifts/index.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16907\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Nature-Conservacy-Gifts.png?resize=600%2C311\" alt=\"Nature Conservacy Gifts\" width=\"600\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Nature-Conservacy-Gifts.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Nature-Conservacy-Gifts.png?resize=300%2C155&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. GlobalGiving Gift Cards</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.globalgiving.org/gifts/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14951 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop-now4\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.globalgiving.org/gifts/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16901\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Global-Giving.png?resize=600%2C344\" alt=\"Global Giving\" width=\"600\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Global-Giving.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Global-Giving.png?resize=300%2C172&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. DonorsChoose.org Gift Cards</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.donorschoose.org/donors/giftoptions.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14951 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop-now4\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.donorschoose.org/donors/giftoptions.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16911\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/DonorsChoose.png?resize=600%2C242\" alt=\"DonorsChoose\" width=\"600\" height=\"242\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/DonorsChoose.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/DonorsChoose.png?resize=300%2C121&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Compassion International Gift Catalog</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.compassion.com/catalog.htm?referer=132736\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14951\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop-now4\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.compassion.com/catalog.htm?referer=132736\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16816\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Compassion-International.png?resize=600%2C389\" alt=\"Compassion International\" width=\"600\" height=\"389\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Compassion-International.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Compassion-International.png?resize=300%2C194&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\" http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/mobile-for-good-with-ribbon.jpg\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
